== 组织结构 ==

'''金融稳定委员会'''设立每年不定期不定点召开两次<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://fsbwatch.org/index.php/the-fsb|title=The Structure of the FSB|accessdate=2014-07-06|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|format=|work=|publisher='''''fsbwatch'''''|pages=|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826104321/http://fsbwatch.org/index.php/the-fsb|archivedate=2013-08-26|quote=The full FSB meets twice a year in Plenary (times and locations are still ad hoc.)|deadurl=yes}}</ref>的全体会议（{{lang-en|Plenary}}）与常设的指导委员会（{{lang-en|Steering Committee}}），而在它们之下又分设三个常设委员会<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://intl.ce.cn/zhuanti/data/jw/jwnews/200906/30/t20090630_1471667.shtml|title=给国际金融穿上"防弹衣" 金融稳定会正式成立|accessdate=2014-07-06|author=王如君、吴成良|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=2009-06-30|year=|month=|format=|work='''''[[中国经济网|中国经济网]]'''''|publisher=[[人民日报|人民日报]]|pages=|language=zh-cn|doi=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706024913/http://intl.ce.cn/zhuanti/data/jw/jwnews/200906/30/t20090630_1471667.shtml|archivedate=2014-07-06|quote=|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，分别为脆弱性评估委员会（SCAV）{{efn|'''脆弱性评估委员会'''（{{lang-en|'''S'''tanding '''C'''ommittee on '''A'''ssessment of '''V'''ulnerabilities}}，简称'''SCAV'''）}}、监管和管理合作委员会（SCSRC）{{efn|'''监管和管理合作委员会'''（{{lang-en|'''S'''tanding '''C'''ommittee on '''S'''upervisory and '''R'''egulatory '''C'''ooperation}}，简称'''SCSRC'''）}}、标准执行委员会（SCSI）{{efn|'''标准执行委员会'''（{{lang-en|'''S'''tanding '''C'''ommittee on '''S'''tandards '''I'''mplementation}}，简称'''SCSI'''）}}，后加设<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.financialstabilityboard.org/about/pac.htm|title=FSB Plenary, Committees and Regional Consultative Groups (RCGs) membership|accessdate=2014-07-06|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|format=|work=|publisher='''''Financial Stability Board'''''|pages=|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629135016/http://www.financialstabilityboard.org/about/pac.htm|archivedate=2014-06-29|quote=Lists of the members of the FSB's Plenary, Steering Committee, Standing Committees and RCGs can be found below:……|deadurl=yes}}</ref>资源预算委员会（SCBR）{{efn|'''资源预算委员会'''（{{lang-en|'''S'''tanding '''C'''ommittee on '''B'''udget and '''R'''esources}}，简称'''SCBR'''）}}及6个区域咨询小组（RCGs）{{efn|'''区域咨询小组'''（{{lang-en|'''R'''egional '''C'''onsultative '''G'''roups}}，简称'''RCGs'''）}}。

